title: Old fashioned pumpkin loaf cake
ingredients: ['500g cooked pumpkin, mashed well', '4 eggs, beaten', '175ml vegetable oil', '120ml water', '500g plain flour', '1 teaspoon salt', '600g sugar', '2 teaspoons bicarb of soda', '1 teaspoon ground cinnamon', '1/2 teaspoon ground nutmeg', '1/2 teaspoon ground ginger']
